paper_assembly.combined_prompt:
You are an expert in ontology and knowledge-graph merging. Below are subgraphs from each paper section. Merge them into one comprehensive JSON knowledge graph with a top-level ["Paper"] node connected to each section node (e.g. 'HAS_SECTION'). In the ["Paper"] node's properties, include:

"agent_prompts": {
  "system_prompt": "You are an expert on the entire paper...",
  "example_user_query": "Give me a high-level summary of all sections."
}

Ensure valid JSON only.
